Collected on forest trails near a stream in disturbed secondary forest, and on a ridgetop in primary montane forest; at elevations of 
<quantity id="036C9B1BFF6D6AD2FC909D5B1A18B011" box="[876,1048,2818,2851]" metricMagnitude="3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.0" metricValueMax="1.6" metricValueMin="0.4" pageId="150" pageNumber="911" unit="m" value="1000.0" valueMax="1600.0" valueMin="400.0">400-1600 m</quantity>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
