<subSubSection id="8C8E6575FF6D6AD2FF8E9D9E1C2AB705" pageId="150" pageNumber="911" type="conservation">
<paragraph id="C42B36FEFF6D6AD2FF8E9D9E1C2AB705" blockId="150.[112,1319,2194,3166]" pageId="150" pageNumber="911">
<emphasis id="F6E0EAECFF6D6AD2FF8E9D9E1FCDB0DA" bold="true" box="[114,461,3015,3048]" pageId="150" pageNumber="911">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Not assessed on The IUCN RedLust, as it is included in Scully’s Tube-nosed Bat (
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF6D6AD2FE9F9DAB1C0CB73D" baseAuthorityName="Scully" baseAuthorityYear="1881" box="[355,524,3058,3087]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Murina" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="150" pageNumber="911" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="tubinaris">M. tubinaris</taxonomicName>
), which is listed as Least Concern. Currently known only from four localities in 
<collectingCountry id="BC83766EFF6D6AD2FE579A4F1C25B705" box="[427,549,3094,3127]" name="Vietnam" pageId="150" pageNumber="911">Vietnam</collectingCountry>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
